ted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2271500/extras/bd6e8b08b381c8e95cabde7e00a3e96e.poster.avif?t=1770890040\" width=544 height=170 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2271500/extras/bd6e8b08b381c8e95cabde7e00a3e96e.webm?t=1770890040\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2271500/extras/bd6e8b08b381c8e95cabde7e00a3e96e.mp4?t=1770890040\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2271500/extras/443c1e10266c559c15bc6c48ec8c29fb.avif?t=1770890040\" width=544 height=100 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2271500/extras/11dca31b5656dfaaa08691d9d2b4767d.poster.avif?t=1770890040\" width=544 height=170 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2271500/extras/11dca31b5656dfaaa08691d9d2b4767d.webm?t=1770890040\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2271500/extras/11dca31b5656dfaaa08691d9d2b4767d.mp4?t=1770890040\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Emplacement 是一款创新的战略性回合制游戏，结合了铺设和战斗元素。每位玩家在等距游戏盘上轮流放置模块以获得战胜对手的优势。类似于国际象棋，玩家必须提前谋略，成功预测对手的下一步方可获胜。<br><br>随着游戏的进行，玩家带领自己的兵将与对方作战，消灭敌军国王，取得最终胜利。游戏开始时，国王应放置在游戏盘的特殊位置，并受其将领的保护。成功杀死其他玩家的国王，即可赢得游戏。<br><br>Emplacement是一款具有挑战性和娱乐性的游戏，玩家需要发挥其最佳创造力和战略性思考。该游戏的等距视角和回合制游戏玩法增加了体验的深度和刺激性，使其成为战略游戏迷的必玩之作。该游戏简单且引人入胜的机制适合所有年龄段和技能水平的玩家，使其成为休闲和铁杆玩家的绝佳选择。",
